1. virtualenv
   set up a virtual environment
   virtualenv --distribute venv
   activate a virtual enviornment:#source venv/bin/activiate
   deactivate a virtual environment: in virtualenv, >>>>deactivate

2. sqlite for protyping
   eg. CREATE TABLE todo (id integer primary key, title text, created date, done boolean default 'f');
   insert into todo (title) values ('Learn web.py');

3. web.py support sqlite3. sqlite2.x will not work with the latest web.py.


